      "kind": "content",
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "discussion",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Using a content configuration, you can set the view’s content and styling for a variety of different view states. You can get the default configuration using "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/uikit/uitableviewheaderfooterview/3600597-defaultcontentconfiguration"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ", assign your content to the configuration, customize any other properties, and assign it to the view as the current "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/uikit/uitableviewheaderfooterview/3600596-contentconfiguration"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Setting a content configuration replaces the existing "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/uikit/uitableviewheaderfooterview/1624914-contentview"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " of the view with a new content view instance from the configuration, or directly applies the configuration to the existing content view if the configuration is compatible with the existing content view type."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The default value is "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "nil"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ". After you set a content configuration to this property, setting this property back to "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "nil"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " replaces the current content view with a new, empty content view."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": []
        }
      ]
    }
